description.en: DefPace is a brand that aims to offer a wide variety of play-to-earn NFT games on a single platform.  This enables users to have multiple play-to-earn options to choose from. The users are able to purchase NFT Characters which they will be able to use to play our games and earn tokens. The project will also have a marketplace for users to buy or sell, we will be releasing new characters regularly for users to collect and use.
